<p>
  <big>Sound Options:</big><br/><br/>
<i>* Enable sounds for events<br/></i>
  <small>
  When checked you can select different sounds &#x28;.wav files&#x29; that will be played at different
  times when using the browser. To disable or enable a specific sound check or uncheck the box at that
  sound event. Select sounds by clicking on the &#x22;Open Folder&#x22; button to the right sound of
  each sound event. You can listen to the sound by pressing the &#x22;Arrow&#x22; button to the right
  of the open button.<br/>
  <br/>
  WinWAP comes preloaded with default sounds for each event.
  </small>
<br/><br/>

